For international residents:
TRIPBFF LLC is headquartered in the United States of America. It and its authorized processors may transfer your information to the United States of America and access it from the Unites States of America for the Purposes described in this Policy. TRIPBFF LLC protects the privacy and security of Personal Information in the manner described in this Policy regardless of where it is collected, stored, accessed, or otherwise Processed.
Does this Policy ever change?
TRIPBFF LLC may post changes to this Policy on this page.¬† Please refer to the ‚Äúlast updated‚Äù date above.¬† We may or may not contact you directly concerning significant changes, and therefore we encourage you to visit this page periodically and check.¬† By using TRIPBFF LLC products and services after a change to this Policy, you are deemed to consent to any changes.
